Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我零用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要给他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 要很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真给他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.17,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H0203C6&\pos(433.5,38)}大塚村的恶梦再袭！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.17,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正隶变_GBK\frz271\pos(1210,342)}出现怪病？复活的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.17,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正隶变_GBK\frz270.8\pos(1125,345)}本应死亡的五人接连复活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道关于这个事件的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体的情况我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闯入禁忌之山的五个村民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回来后的一周后 全部死于谜样的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地区也有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是少有甘霖的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他背靠着一座被称为「外持」的山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如其名只有外持之山 会下「外持之雨」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外持？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓「外持」就是指特别对待的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那鱼就像一个人突然得到意外的好处一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 将只润泽特定地区的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做「外持之雨」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降在那座山上的雨变成地下水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总能让我们顺利种植作物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近连那水源也干涸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位是乐师大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您特意邀我们到此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 发生了那种事件我还以为你们不会来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是难得的村祭 想要办得华丽些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请随我去村长家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旦开野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.14,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.14,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:59.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:59.52,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:04.02,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:04.02,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:10.32,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:10.32,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹着干燥的风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:16.79,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:16.79,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真伪 铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:20.21,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:20.21,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈愿待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.92,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.92,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱过 恨过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.46,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.46,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲伤最后化作温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:31.43,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:31.43,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入无尽黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:36.26,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:36.26,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍会寻觅明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:40.39,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:40.39,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃烧的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:45.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:45.52,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之缘 最终转化成奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.57,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.57,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.15,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.15,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:53.45,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:53.45,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拨开黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:57.62,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:57.62,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追寻你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.00,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.00,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.46,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.46,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总有一天 命运将会转变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:08.17,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:08.17,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要让眼泪白流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:12.84,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:12.84,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交织骚动的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.39,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.39,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狂吠吧 交织的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个男人为了寻找新的水源进入了山中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那里禁止进入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村中流传着那座山中自古以来住着猿神的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅入者有去无回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这五人却回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徘徊在山中 即将饿死之际
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说出现了一位美丽的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人为五人指出了回到村里的路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还赠与了他们水喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 就像五年前的大塚村一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人…把水…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里见先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到信乃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到午饭的时间了 却不见他出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他一定会去 没想到一个人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介 马上去追信乃比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是只在这座山中下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明珠在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的和庄介的都在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止发过光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又梦到那个男人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的一切…夺走的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在五年前的大塚村也出现了一个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和信乃 滨路能幸免于难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为陪伴健康状况崩溃的信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在邻村的疗养所疗养的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行 记忆一片模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来送客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你在找信乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他坐上了去西边的电车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是擅自跑出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他要去哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我正要去追他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去追信乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 不要突然出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一班西行的列车还要等两个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一副干劲十足的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去厨房准备些便当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他丢下你一个人去的地方 说明不是什么好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带两只鬼过去 可以充当保镖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是让人安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说我们所前往的山里会出现猿神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 又扯上怪物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介的玉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到和这个一样的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的青梅竹马寄放在我这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是丢了的话 就麻烦了
